Package soc.code.multiplayerPackage

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ClientConnection
    This class is responsible for handling one connection to one client.
    ClientSetup
    This class is meant to handle the multiplayer connection to the host for this client.
    ConnectionHelper
    This class is for housing helper methods to assist in data spitting and data sucking via sockets and server sockets.
    DataSucker
    This class' purpose is to suck up all the lines of incoming data that it can from a given socket and store all that data in an ArrayList of Strings.
    HostSetup
    This class is responsible for storing and keeping track of all the client connection objects.
